('71aad405-dde6-4f08-9686-493aa5136dce', 'credit-theft-social-psychosynt-30', 'social', 'Credit theft (social)', 'A colleague presents your idea as their own in a room that matters. Correcting it risks looking petty; staying silent cedes the win. The clock is running.'),
