('4146d822-6be2-4d43-812d-4dd46befaca9', 'exclusion-social-psychosynt-34', 'social', 'Exclusion (social)', 'You learn the group made plans without you and did not think to mention it. Raising it seems needy; swallowing it seeds resentment.'),
('0703e6f4-525b-41b1-89d5-72357949a2e6', 'layoff-call-crisis-psychosynt-35', 'crisis', 'Layoff call (crisis)', 'Numbers demand cutting 54% of the team by Friday. Moving fast is cleaner; agonizing over each name is humane but paralyzing. There is no clean option.'),
